MySql New Columns and Data Injection

To insert new columns to anahita table an_people_people without packages (not a permanent solution)
	1. You must update code in two locations
		1. anahita/src/components/com_anahita/schemas/migrations/19.php
		2. anahita/vendor/anahita-platform/installation/sql/schema.sql
	2. Find the sections of Code that reference an_people_people
	3. Insert Column names and types following the same conventions used around them
	4. Save Changes and restart database with changes

